    <title>Writing in the text area of CWRC-Writer by selecting a tag</title>
    <shortdesc>There are multiple ways to begin writing text in CWRC-Writer. You can select a tag
        and then begin to write, or you can place your cursor in the editor and begin to type. </shortdesc>
